  "time_ut": 1657009430,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fishing in a sailboat due to lack of fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to lack of fuel, many of the Kilinochchi fishermen have started the sailing boat business as per the ancient method.",
        "They say that they can only get a small amount of income through this.",
        "They also say that they have started engaging in coastal fishing by tying bedsheets, sari and strong cloth in their boats, and they express concern that Indian trawlers are engaging in maritime activities in front of their eyes in their sea.",
        "Thousands of fishermen in Kilinochchi have lost their livelihood due to lack of fuel.",
        "Fishermen from Poonagri, Palai and Kandawela are unable to get the fuel they need for their business activities.",
        "The fishermen informed that no one has taken any action in this regard even though they have brought it to the attention of many people, and they realized that if they continue to wait for fuel by trusting the responsible people, their families will have no means of food.",
        "Therefore, Kilinochchi fishermen said that they have switched to ancient fishing methods."
      ],
